      <subsection name="Vision">
        <p>This vision of mmm is to build an ECMS with 
        <a href="mmm-content/index.html">mmm-content</a> on top of the 
        <a href="mmm-framework/index.html">mmm-framework</a> using the 
        <a href="mmm-uit/index.html">mmm-uit</a> and all the other useful modules.</p>
        <p>There is still a long way to go. Anyhow the first sub-projects are about
        to be released soon. This will include <a href="mmm-search/index.html">mmm-search</a>
        and according parts of <a href="mmm-util/index.html">mmm-util</a>.</p>
        <p>The mmm-uit needs intensive improvements and web-support, etc.</p>
        <p>The ECMS content module (OO-database layer) is NOT yet available.
        It is still unclear if JCR (JSR 170) will be used as generic API, because it sucks.
        </p>
